description: Las Quinas is an innovative initiative that combines organic honey production with social responsibility. Founded by a former corporate professional, the company collaborates with local producers and cooperatives, fostering trust and mutual benefits. Over the years, Las Quinas has expanded its product line to include dulce de leche and jams, while also engaging in community projects that empower vulnerable groups, particularly women. Their commitment to sustainability and social impact has garnered recognition both locally and internationally.
name: Las Quinas
